OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772881499
OL,3,CThree women questioned as part of
OL,4,Cabuse investigation into Mohamed Al
OL,5,CFayed
OL,7,FThree women have been questioned by
OL,8,Fpolice over allegations of human
OL,9,Ftrafficking and facilitating rape as
OL,10,Fpart of an investigation into former
OL,11,FHarrods boss Mohamed Al Fayed.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police said on Friday
OL,14,Fthat 154 victims have come forward and
OL,15,Freported allegations of sexual
OL,16,Fassault, rape, sexual exploitation and
OL,17,Fhuman trafficking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
