PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772881499
OL,3,CThree women questioned as part of
OL,4,Cabuse investigation into Mohamed Al
OL,5,CFayed
OL,7,FThe three women, who were not
OL,8,Farrested, were questioned between
OL,9,FWednesday February 25 and Thursday
OL,10,FMarch 5 on suspicion of assisting the
OL,11,Fcommission of sexual offences.
OL,13,FNo arrests have been made and the
OL,14,Finvestigation, which has been
OL,15,Fbroadened to cover human trafficking
OL,16,Ffollowing calls from survivors, is
OL,17,Fongoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
