OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772881499
OL,3,CThree women questioned as part of
OL,4,Cabuse investigation into Mohamed Al
OL,5,CFayed
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FCommander Angela Craggs of the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police said: "Victims
OL,14,Fremain at the centre of this
OL,15,Finvestigation. Today's update marks an
OL,16,Fimportant step in a complex and far
OL,17,Freaching investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
