PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772881499
OL,3,CThree women questioned as part of
OL,4,Cabuse investigation into Mohamed Al
OL,5,CFayed
OL,7,F"While Al Fayed is no longer alive to
OL,8,Fface prosecution, we have always been
OL,9,Fdetermined to bring anyone who is
OL,10,Fsuspected to have played a part in his
OL,11,Foffending to justice.
OL,13,F"We encourage anyone with information,
OL,14,Fwhether you were directly affected by
OL,15,FMohamed Al Fayed actions or have
OL,16,Fconcerns about others who may have
OL,17,Fbeen involved or committed offences,
OL,18,Fto contact us. Information can also be
OL,19,Fshared anonymously with Crimestoppers
OL,20,Fon 0800 555 111 or through their
OL,21,Fonline form.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
