OL,3,CThree women questioned as part of
OL,4,Cabuse investigation into Mohamed Al
OL,5,CFayed
OL,7,F"We will share further updates when we
OL,8,Fare able to do so and only when this
OL,9,Fwill not risk jeopardising criminal or
OL,10,Fother proceedings."
